Ask HN: Do you care about tech anymore?
text: For some reason I find that I just don't care about tech at all. Something happened in last year that completely killed it. Just how I couldn't care less that what type of exhaust is the best for certain type of motor bikes... Similarly don't care about compiler speed, output size, execution speed, etc. Almost like realizing that none of it matters it's not your choice what you use. The more you succeed in your career the less choices you have because you end up at bigger companies and taking 50% pay cut for new stack doesn't make sense
